{"tid":579090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊撚個扯斷大番薯啲頭髮","createTime":"2018-03-03T09:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T10:00:07.000Z","uid":55725,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84a0b7254bc9eaeef095ea180d76241af765a165","tid":579090,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，開張嘅時候我同女朋友討論大番薯一個禮拜之後唔見幾多條頭髮，一個禮拜之後其中一條頭髮換咗做一支黑色飲管都算<br />\n而家連支黑色飲管都無埋，得番個窿係到<br />\n大番薯頭髮得果三條，邊條仆街咁無品手多整斷大番薯既頭髮，死出黎負責任啦<br />\n根據 《刑事罪行條例》 第60條 ，任何人如無合法辯解而摧毀或損壞他人財產，意圖作出上述行為，或罔顧他人財產被摧毀或損壞而作出上述行為，都屬違法，最高可被判終身監禁。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/171923_7ae2ddb1b397093ebfbf39a99c753372.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F171923_7ae2ddb1b397093ebfbf39a99c753372.jpeg&h=fa4faa9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c640529d1cb17deb1b7fa40e45ef7194613d868","tid":579090,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"唔比佢老咗自己甩？<br />\n唔好篤穿人帶假髮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c4c4300b08131dc48239ecb6d2b8461bddf528","tid":579090,"uid":116143,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0c640529d1cb17deb1b7fa40e45ef7194613d868","tid":579090,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"唔比佢老咗自己甩？<br />\n唔好篤穿人帶假髮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"幽默嘅野無得強求&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"405851585fdc13f9f934925897f8c918592446a4","tid":579090,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72c4c4300b08131dc48239ecb6d2b8461bddf528","tid":579090,"uid":116143,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0c640529d1cb17deb1b7fa40e45ef7194613d868","tid":579090,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"唔比佢老咗自己甩？<br /